WEBVTT

00:01:36.070 --> 00:01:38.289
[Too Young To Love]

00:01:38.470 --> 00:01:41.250
[Episode 9]

00:01:46.490 --> 00:01:48.509
[Updates on your application
to the Malayan Conservatory of Music]

00:01:51.750 --> 00:01:52.350
Why did my scholarship application
get rejected again?

00:01:52.350 --> 00:01:55.620
[Updates on your application
to the Malayan Conservatory of Music]

00:02:27.670 --> 00:02:32.130
[I have wrestled with myself for long.
I'd rather just be me.]

00:02:36.910 --> 00:02:37.590
Xiaole!

00:02:38.190 --> 00:02:39.190
Tong Xiaole!

00:02:47.030 --> 00:02:47.829
What's wrong?

00:02:48.079 --> 00:02:49.079
Come downstairs.

00:02:49.120 --> 00:02:50.720
I want to show you something.

00:02:55.800 --> 00:02:56.400
What is it?

00:02:56.840 --> 00:02:57.800
Come here. Come here.

00:02:57.800 --> 00:02:59.400
I want to show you something.

00:02:59.470 --> 00:03:00.190
It's raining.

00:03:00.190 --> 00:03:01.470
Just come here. Hurry.

00:03:03.840 --> 00:03:04.590
What?

00:03:06.750 --> 00:03:07.430
Look.

00:03:09.280 --> 00:03:10.010
Do you see it?

00:03:11.280 --> 00:03:13.140
My calluses have been rubbed raw.

00:03:13.680 --> 00:03:14.870
What does this prove?

00:03:14.870 --> 00:03:16.800
It proves that on the path to success,

00:03:16.800 --> 00:03:18.660
I've taken another step forward.

00:03:19.079 --> 00:03:19.910
For this,

00:03:19.910 --> 00:03:21.710
you called me downstairs

00:03:22.000 --> 00:03:23.310
to stand here in the rain with you?

00:03:23.310 --> 00:03:24.710
I'm happy. What's wrong with that?

00:03:24.710 --> 00:03:25.280
Fine.

00:03:25.280 --> 00:03:26.960
It indeed is worth celebrating.

00:03:26.960 --> 00:03:28.190
Then I wish you success

00:03:28.190 --> 00:03:29.750
in passing the joint exam.

00:03:30.240 --> 00:03:30.680
Okay.

00:03:34.800 --> 00:03:35.850
Thanks to my hard work,

00:03:35.850 --> 00:03:35.910
[Hailan University School Exam Day
Go for it]

00:03:35.910 --> 00:03:37.870
I successfully passed the joint exam.

00:03:37.870 --> 00:03:38.630
Next,

00:03:38.630 --> 00:03:41.160
it'll be
the even more difficult school exam.

00:03:45.150 --> 00:03:45.800
Lan.

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:49.000
During the exam,

00:03:49.360 --> 00:03:50.360
don't be nervous.

00:03:51.150 --> 00:03:52.410
Just perform as usual.

00:03:52.470 --> 00:03:52.910
Okay.

00:03:53.400 --> 00:03:54.030
Sister,

00:03:54.560 --> 00:03:56.150
you will definitely pass.

00:03:56.520 --> 00:03:57.120
Good luck.

00:03:57.360 --> 00:03:58.000
Okay.

00:03:58.520 --> 00:03:59.190
You really don't need me

00:03:59.190 --> 00:04:00.450
to take you to the exam?

00:04:01.000 --> 00:04:01.800
No need, Dad.

00:04:02.080 --> 00:04:03.740
Xiaole will come to pick me up.

00:04:09.030 --> 00:04:09.750
I'm off! I'm off!

00:04:09.750 --> 00:04:10.210
Bye bye!

00:04:12.430 --> 00:04:12.960
Let's go!

00:04:15.590 --> 00:04:16.790
Everything's ready?

00:04:18.000 --> 00:04:18.459
Not yet.

00:04:20.720 --> 00:04:21.310
I want to make a wish.

00:04:21.310 --> 00:04:22.310
Give me your hand.

00:04:23.360 --> 00:04:24.360
Make a wish.

00:04:25.950 --> 00:04:26.560
Bless me.

00:04:27.040 --> 00:04:29.040
Pass on the top student's luck to me.

00:04:29.240 --> 00:04:31.720
If you're going to make a wish,
do it properly.

00:04:31.720 --> 00:04:32.650
Close your eyes.

00:04:38.480 --> 00:04:39.040
Done.

00:04:40.070 --> 00:04:41.390
You already
have the top student's blessing.

00:04:41.390 --> 00:04:43.320
You definitely will pass the exam.

00:04:43.390 --> 00:04:43.830
Let's go.

00:04:43.830 --> 00:04:44.360
Let's go.

00:04:47.830 --> 00:04:48.480
Bundle up.

00:04:48.480 --> 00:04:49.610
It's cold on the way.

00:05:18.750 --> 00:05:19.510
Ning?

00:05:21.160 --> 00:05:23.360
How come you're taking the school exam?

00:05:24.390 --> 00:05:26.120
It was a last-minute decision.

00:05:33.750 --> 00:05:35.210
Something came up at home.

00:05:35.510 --> 00:05:39.070
My scholarship application
for the overseas university failed.

00:05:39.070 --> 00:05:40.930
The school exam is my only way out.

00:05:46.070 --> 00:05:47.390
Why are you wearing so little?

00:05:47.390 --> 00:05:48.320
Aren't you cold?

00:05:49.390 --> 00:05:50.000
Warm up.

00:05:55.510 --> 00:05:56.750
You don't think

00:05:57.720 --> 00:05:59.310
I was lying to you before, do you?

00:05:59.310 --> 00:06:00.190
Why would I?

00:06:01.000 --> 00:06:01.950
Since you didn't say anything,

00:06:01.950 --> 00:06:03.680
I'm sure you have your reasons.

00:06:03.830 --> 00:06:04.560
Don't worry.

00:06:04.630 --> 00:06:05.950
I'll keep your secret.

00:06:07.630 --> 00:06:08.390
Anyway,

00:06:08.750 --> 00:06:10.680
