00:06:11.000 --> 00:06:12.730
you'll shine wherever you are.

00:06:12.870 --> 00:06:13.800
I believe in you.

00:06:16.040 --> 00:06:17.560
Actually, I...

00:06:17.830 --> 00:06:20.030
Whenever you're unhappy, just tell me.

00:06:20.160 --> 00:06:22.160
You don't have to tough it out alone.

00:06:26.160 --> 00:06:26.870
Thank you.

00:06:29.310 --> 00:06:30.310
Let's do our best.

00:06:30.630 --> 00:06:31.490
We've got this.

00:06:31.920 --> 00:06:32.780
I'm so nervous.

00:06:37.920 --> 00:06:39.270
During the one-month winter break,

00:06:39.270 --> 00:06:41.159
don't get too carried away!

00:06:41.270 --> 00:06:42.190
Take care!

00:06:42.190 --> 00:06:43.060
Bye bye.

00:06:43.080 --> 00:06:43.870
Alright, alright!

00:06:43.870 --> 00:06:44.640
Get going, everyone!

00:06:44.640 --> 00:06:45.310
Come. Come.

00:06:45.310 --> 00:06:46.310
Give me the stuff.

00:06:46.990 --> 00:06:47.640
Bye bye.

00:06:47.640 --> 00:06:48.230
Alright.

00:06:48.250 --> 00:06:48.990
Bye bye.

00:06:49.190 --> 00:06:50.430
Be careful when you leave later.

00:06:50.430 --> 00:06:52.030
-Turn off the lights.
-Okay.

00:06:52.750 --> 00:06:55.110
You two, how do you plan
to spend the winter break?

00:06:55.110 --> 00:06:55.920
I don't know.

00:06:56.190 --> 00:06:56.840
Lan,

00:06:56.920 --> 00:06:59.280
I heard Ning went to Hailan University
for the art exam.

00:06:59.280 --> 00:07:00.410
Did you run into her?

00:07:00.670 --> 00:07:01.400
Yes, I did.

00:07:03.670 --> 00:07:05.530
Wasn't she going to study abroad?

00:07:06.990 --> 00:07:08.550
I'm not too sure about that.

00:07:08.670 --> 00:07:10.430
Then we should just ask Ning.

00:07:10.920 --> 00:07:11.850
We'd better not.

00:07:12.010 --> 00:07:13.990
She'll tell us if she wants to.

00:07:14.160 --> 00:07:15.130
Let's not pry.

00:07:15.360 --> 00:07:16.480
Yi Lan is right.

00:07:16.480 --> 00:07:18.240
It indeed is not polite to ask directly.

00:07:18.240 --> 00:07:21.130
But Hailan University is pretty good too.

00:07:21.890 --> 00:07:23.300
I'll go ask Bu

00:07:23.480 --> 00:07:25.810
how to get admitted to Hailan University.

00:07:27.450 --> 00:07:27.890
Lan.

00:07:29.400 --> 00:07:30.130
Look at this.

00:07:30.240 --> 00:07:30.300
I recently discovered

00:07:30.300 --> 00:07:31.240
[L Photography]

00:07:31.240 --> 00:07:33.280
