00:07:33.280 --> 00:07:35.340
Look, this photo looks just like you.

00:07:35.600 --> 00:07:36.450
Me?

00:07:38.040 --> 00:07:39.440
It does look a bit like me.

00:07:39.920 --> 00:07:41.280
Isn't this our school?

00:07:41.360 --> 00:07:41.800
Yeah.

00:07:43.090 --> 00:07:45.290
Beauties all have something in common.

00:07:46.360 --> 00:07:46.970
Ning.

00:07:51.600 --> 00:07:55.280
My mom brought this back from abroad.

00:07:55.530 --> 00:07:57.240
I heard you really like

00:07:57.360 --> 00:07:58.720
this brand of chocolate,

00:07:58.720 --> 00:07:59.800
so I...

00:08:11.600 --> 00:08:13.210
I have wrestled with myself for long.

00:08:13.210 --> 00:08:14.410
I'd rather just be me.

00:08:14.480 --> 00:08:16.130
I really like that quote too.

00:08:16.920 --> 00:08:18.580
I think you're truly amazing.

00:08:19.160 --> 00:08:20.040
No matter where you go,

00:08:20.040 --> 00:08:21.570
I think you'll always be...

00:08:21.970 --> 00:08:23.160
the best.

00:08:25.570 --> 00:08:26.530
So...

00:08:30.160 --> 00:08:30.970
Thank you.

00:08:48.090 --> 00:08:50.820
My mom's performance
is absolutely incredible.

00:08:51.410 --> 00:08:52.360
I need to work hard too.

00:08:52.360 --> 00:08:53.290
I must do my best.

00:08:54.930 --> 00:08:57.090
Then I'll restore these recordings

00:08:57.210 --> 00:08:58.760
and turn them into vinyl records.

00:08:58.760 --> 00:08:59.840
You can keep them as souvenirs

00:08:59.840 --> 00:09:01.570
and listen to them whenever you want.

00:09:01.570 --> 00:09:02.690
You're so nice,

00:09:02.690 --> 00:09:03.690
Shan!

00:09:05.640 --> 00:09:06.770
Time to do homework.

00:09:18.000 --> 00:09:18.840
Who is it?

00:09:20.480 --> 00:09:21.240
Listen.

00:09:21.240 --> 00:09:22.810
I've been following
a photography blogger recently.

00:09:22.810 --> 00:09:23.940
He's super amazing.

00:09:25.290 --> 00:09:27.750
Mengmeng insisted
this photo looks like me.

00:09:29.760 --> 00:09:30.620
It does seem...

00:09:30.880 --> 00:09:32.080
a little bit like you.

00:09:32.240 --> 00:09:33.600
And I feel this person

00:09:33.600 --> 00:09:35.120
must be very close to us.

00:09:36.050 --> 00:09:37.240
Someone around us.

00:09:37.450 --> 00:09:38.000
Look.

00:09:38.000 --> 00:09:39.570
This is the breakfast shop,

00:09:39.970 --> 00:09:40.640
coffee shop,

00:09:40.640 --> 00:09:41.410
and the street we usually go to.

00:09:41.410 --> 00:09:43.000
They are exactly the same as where we go.

00:09:43.000 --> 00:09:44.930
The photos are quite artistic too.

00:09:49.240 --> 00:09:50.970
I also discovered a big secret.

00:09:51.760 --> 00:09:52.410
Look.

00:09:52.600 --> 00:09:54.210
He pinned the photo of this girl's back

00:09:54.210 --> 00:09:54.880
