00:09:56.480 --> 00:09:57.610
What does that mean?

00:09:58.000 --> 00:09:59.600
What... does that mean?

00:09:59.600 --> 00:10:01.360
He has a secret crush on her.

00:10:02.410 --> 00:10:04.120
And this person

00:10:04.120 --> 00:10:05.600
must be from our school.

00:10:05.880 --> 00:10:07.330
Look at the hem of the school uniform.

00:10:07.330 --> 00:10:09.790
It's exactly the same
as our school uniform.

00:10:09.840 --> 00:10:10.840
Nowadays,

00:10:11.410 --> 00:10:13.090
