are pretty much the same.

00:10:13.090 --> 00:10:14.690
There's no real difference.

00:10:14.930 --> 00:10:16.190
You don't understand.

00:10:16.410 --> 00:10:16.970
Stop looking.

00:10:16.970 --> 00:10:18.700
Hurry up and do your questions.

00:10:19.240 --> 00:10:20.600
My phone has no signal.

00:10:20.810 --> 00:10:22.050
Let me use your phone for a look.

00:10:22.050 --> 00:10:23.210
