00:10:24.690 --> 00:10:25.690
You have a secret.

00:10:27.810 --> 00:10:29.520
-Give it to me. Give it to me!
-Go back and do your questions!

00:10:29.520 --> 00:10:30.290
Give it to me.

00:10:38.880 --> 00:10:42.000
Three, two, one!

00:10:49.880 --> 00:10:51.640
