00:11:00.640 --> 00:11:01.840
Weirdo.

00:11:07.600 --> 00:11:09.720
Didn't we agree
we couldn't mortgage the house?

00:11:09.720 --> 00:11:11.120
Now we're about to lose the house!

00:11:11.120 --> 00:11:13.780
Do you still want
to have a good Chinese New Year?

00:11:25.470 --> 00:11:25.720
[Reborn! We Got This]

00:11:25.720 --> 00:11:27.240
How about we go to school together
to set off fireworks

00:11:27.240 --> 00:11:28.970
