00:11:29.330 --> 00:11:30.840
Is the second day okay?

00:11:30.970 --> 00:11:33.720
My mom insists on taking me
to Sanya for a few days.

00:11:34.360 --> 00:11:35.240
Mom, stop rushing me.

00:11:35.240 --> 00:11:36.300
I'll be there soon.

00:11:37.050 --> 00:11:37.840
Wait for me.

00:11:42.470 --> 00:11:42.810
[Reborn! We Got This]

00:11:42.810 --> 00:11:43.450
Okay.

00:11:44.410 --> 00:11:45.050
Okay.

00:11:45.090 --> 00:11:46.950
Then let's do it on the second day.

00:11:47.400 --> 00:11:48.330
[Okay. Be well.]

00:11:48.330 --> 00:11:49.970
