00:11:50.930 --> 00:11:51.290
Mm.

00:11:51.290 --> 00:11:51.970
Same as always.

00:11:51.970 --> 00:11:54.100
We plan to eat at Zhonghai Restaurant.

00:11:54.360 --> 00:11:55.290
My family too.

00:11:55.520 --> 00:11:56.330
See you later.

00:11:56.600 --> 00:11:57.240
Lan!

00:11:57.640 --> 00:11:58.480
Hurry up!

00:11:58.880 --> 00:11:59.810
