00:12:09.330 --> 00:12:11.480
Mr. Guo is holding our goods.

00:12:11.720 --> 00:12:13.930
If he doesn't pay,
we'll be in breach of contract.

00:12:13.930 --> 00:12:16.000
Then we won't even be able
to pay salaries.

00:12:16.000 --> 00:12:17.480
Don't offend him again like last time.

00:12:17.480 --> 00:12:18.210
Do you hear me?

00:12:18.210 --> 00:12:18.760
Stop nagging.

00:12:18.760 --> 00:12:19.210
Got it.

00:12:19.410 --> 00:12:20.670
