00:12:21.640 --> 00:12:23.170
I wish everyone...

00:12:24.090 --> 00:12:25.330
great wealth.

00:12:26.240 --> 00:12:27.000
Mr. Guo.

00:12:28.000 --> 00:12:28.600
Mr. Guo.

00:12:28.600 --> 00:12:29.330
Mr. Guo.

00:12:29.330 --> 00:12:30.480
Who's this?

00:12:30.480 --> 00:12:32.600
Let me see! Isn't this Mrs. Tong?

00:12:32.630 --> 00:12:33.240
What a coincidence.

00:12:33.240 --> 00:12:33.760
Mr. Guo.

00:12:33.760 --> 00:12:34.640
I want to eat that.

00:12:34.640 --> 00:12:35.520
I want to eat that.

00:12:35.520 --> 00:12:36.520
I want to eat that!

00:12:38.240 --> 00:12:39.240
I want to eat that!

00:12:40.880 --> 00:12:41.720
See you later.

00:12:46.090 --> 00:12:47.360
I want to eat this.

00:12:47.360 --> 00:12:48.760
I want to eat this.

00:12:48.970 --> 00:12:51.120
Please take care of us
in next year's business.

00:12:51.120 --> 00:12:52.720
-Yes. Yes.
-Take care of you?

00:12:52.840 --> 00:12:54.810
Then I can't let you leave.

00:12:54.810 --> 00:12:55.570
Come on.

00:12:55.840 --> 00:12:56.520
Tong.

00:12:57.090 --> 00:12:57.810
Since we've run into each other,

00:12:57.810 --> 00:12:59.090
and we haven't seen each other in a while,

00:12:59.090 --> 00:12:59.570
