00:13:00.330 --> 00:13:01.930
Have a drink before you leave.

00:13:01.930 --> 00:13:02.640
Okay?

00:13:02.720 --> 00:13:04.120
Tong's been having stomach issues lately.

00:13:04.120 --> 00:13:04.720
I'll drink with you,

00:13:04.720 --> 00:13:05.330
Mr. Guo.

00:13:05.330 --> 00:13:05.720
Come on.

00:13:05.720 --> 00:13:06.480
Long time no see.

00:13:06.480 --> 00:13:06.970
Mrs. Tong.

00:13:06.970 --> 00:13:07.410
Get me a glass.

00:13:07.410 --> 00:13:07.840
You...

00:13:07.840 --> 00:13:08.640
P-Put it down.

00:13:08.880 --> 00:13:09.840
Listen to me.

00:13:10.640 --> 00:13:11.520
While I'm around,

00:13:11.520 --> 00:13:12.880
