00:13:19.880 --> 00:13:20.610
Half a glass.

00:13:20.640 --> 00:13:21.000
Okay.

00:13:21.570 --> 00:13:23.170
-Half a glass.
-I'll down it.

00:13:27.570 --> 00:13:28.170
Chen.

00:13:28.170 --> 00:13:28.760
Good.

00:13:28.760 --> 00:13:29.760
I was right, right?

00:13:29.760 --> 00:13:30.410
But

00:13:30.410 --> 00:13:31.120
