00:13:37.480 --> 00:13:38.210
Okay?

00:13:38.210 --> 00:13:39.240
Let's toast Mr. Tong together.

00:13:39.240 --> 00:13:39.570
Come on.

00:13:39.570 --> 00:13:40.520
Come on. Come on.

00:13:40.880 --> 00:13:42.050
Come on.

00:13:42.290 --> 00:13:43.640
