00:13:43.640 --> 00:13:44.600
Okay. Come on.

00:13:45.000 --> 00:13:45.720
Bottoms up.

00:13:45.720 --> 00:13:46.330
No problem. Right?

00:13:46.330 --> 00:13:47.000
Bottoms up.

00:13:50.970 --> 00:13:51.970
Dad, Mom,

00:13:52.240 --> 00:13:53.520
Aunt, Uncle,

00:13:53.520 --> 00:13:54.640
Lan, Xiao,

00:13:55.050 --> 00:13:56.520
