00:13:58.320 --> 00:13:58.900
Okay.

00:14:18.930 --> 00:14:19.570
Good!

00:14:19.570 --> 00:14:21.170
Good! Good! Good!

00:14:23.210 --> 00:14:24.450
Xuan, you did great.

00:14:24.690 --> 00:14:25.290
Come here.

00:14:28.760 --> 00:14:30.410
I'm giving you a red envelope.

00:14:30.410 --> 00:14:31.600
Keep up the good work.

00:14:31.600 --> 00:14:32.530
Thank you, Aunt.

00:14:33.480 --> 00:14:34.090
Here.

00:14:34.090 --> 00:14:34.690
Off you go.

00:14:37.120 --> 00:14:38.240
Dad, Auntie,

00:14:38.810 --> 00:14:39.610
Aunt,

00:14:39.840 --> 00:14:40.480
Uncle,

00:14:40.810 --> 00:14:41.410
Xiao,

00:14:41.410 --> 00:14:43.170
I'm also going to show you something.

00:14:43.170 --> 00:14:43.840
Okay.

00:15:46.120 --> 00:15:46.760
Good.

00:15:49.210 --> 00:15:50.090
Lan,

00:15:50.450 --> 00:15:52.450
did you just miss two notes?

00:15:54.090 --> 00:15:56.090
How many hours do you practice a day?

00:16:00.970 --> 00:16:02.700
Can she get admitted like this?

00:16:04.000 --> 00:16:04.760
Sister,

00:16:05.410 --> 00:16:06.810
the exam is already over.

00:16:07.640 --> 00:16:08.120
Well,

00:16:08.330 --> 00:16:10.240
Lan has been nervous around you
since she was little.

00:16:10.240 --> 00:16:10.900
Well, look.

00:16:14.480 --> 00:16:15.210
Xiao,

00:16:15.840 --> 00:16:17.090
here's a red envelope from me.

00:16:17.090 --> 00:16:17.360
Here.

00:16:17.360 --> 00:16:18.240
Here. Here.

00:16:18.240 --> 00:16:18.640
Here.

00:16:18.840 --> 00:16:19.360
Thank your uncle.

00:16:19.360 --> 00:16:19.880
Thank you, Uncle.

00:16:19.880 --> 00:16:21.480
It's nothing. It's nothing.

00:16:21.720 --> 00:16:22.480
Sister...

00:16:22.930 --> 00:16:23.530
Let's eat.

00:16:23.720 --> 00:16:24.360
Eat.

00:16:24.360 --> 00:16:24.720
Okay,

00:16:24.720 --> 00:16:25.410
let's eat.

00:16:25.480 --> 00:16:26.120
Lan, come.

00:16:26.120 --> 00:16:26.720
Let's eat.

00:16:29.410 --> 00:16:30.880
Here, Tong.

00:16:31.120 --> 00:16:32.870
Let's drink red wine this time.

00:16:33.290 --> 00:16:34.760
I've learned a new skill—

00:16:34.880 --> 00:16:35.740
mixing drinks.

00:16:36.930 --> 00:16:38.600
Red wine and baijiu

00:16:38.600 --> 00:16:39.600
together.

00:16:41.290 --> 00:16:42.050
Mix them and drink.

00:16:42.050 --> 00:16:42.510
Come on.

00:16:42.520 --> 00:16:42.980
Come on.

00:16:44.360 --> 00:16:44.970
Dad.

00:16:47.760 --> 00:16:48.480
What are you doing here?

00:16:48.480 --> 00:16:49.280
Don't, don't.

00:16:49.600 --> 00:16:50.760
Mr. Guo, right?

00:16:51.000 --> 00:16:51.720
I'll

00:16:51.720 --> 00:16:54.050
drink this toast to you
on behalf of my dad.

00:16:54.360 --> 00:16:54.640
Wait a minute!

00:16:54.640 --> 00:16:55.000
Wait a minute! Wait a minute!

00:16:55.000 --> 00:16:55.560
Tong.

00:16:55.690 --> 00:16:56.810
The one you always talk about...

00:16:56.810 --> 00:16:57.120
The one named...

00:16:57.120 --> 00:16:57.600
Xiaole.

00:16:57.600 --> 00:16:59.170
Xiaole, the top scorer
in the high school entrance exam, right?

00:16:59.170 --> 00:16:59.810
Yes, yes.

00:17:00.330 --> 00:17:02.190
Call him Mr. Guo. Call him Mr. Guo.

00:17:02.480 --> 00:17:03.480
Hello, Xiaole.

00:17:03.760 --> 00:17:04.369
What?

00:17:04.520 --> 00:17:05.650
Xiaole wants to drink?

00:17:05.650 --> 00:17:06.760
He'll have to learn sooner or later.

00:17:06.760 --> 00:17:08.040
Like father, like son.

00:17:08.280 --> 00:17:08.800
How about this?

00:17:08.800 --> 00:17:09.800
If you drink it...

00:17:09.800 --> 00:17:10.690
If you drink with me,

00:17:10.690 --> 00:17:12.130
I will give you a big red envelope.

00:17:12.130 --> 00:17:13.130
Kids can't drink alcohol.

00:17:13.130 --> 00:17:13.930
He can handle it.

00:17:13.930 --> 00:17:14.930
He'll have to learn sooner or later.

00:17:14.930 --> 00:17:15.410
Come on!

00:17:15.650 --> 00:17:16.000
Let...

00:17:16.000 --> 00:17:17.060
Let your son drink!

00:17:19.849 --> 00:17:21.760
Such a mess!

00:17:21.760 --> 00:17:24.000
So ominous during Chinese New Year!

00:17:24.000 --> 00:17:24.970
This... This...

00:17:24.970 --> 00:17:26.079
This is outrageous.

00:17:26.079 --> 00:17:26.800
Look at your child.

00:17:26.800 --> 00:17:27.970
You've spoiled him too much.

00:17:27.970 --> 00:17:28.610
It's Chinese New Year.

00:17:28.610 --> 00:17:29.450
This...

00:17:29.720 --> 00:17:30.520
Dad, get up.

00:17:30.520 --> 00:17:31.580
What are you doing?

00:17:32.040 --> 00:17:32.650
Dad!

00:17:33.000 --> 00:17:33.850
Can't you see this person

00:17:33.850 --> 00:17:36.650
is deliberately making things
difficult for you?

00:17:43.520 --> 00:17:44.080
Stop.

00:17:50.210 --> 00:17:51.670
What were you yelling for?

00:17:53.280 --> 00:17:55.520
Today we're here for the reunion dinner.

00:17:55.520 --> 00:17:57.980
How long has it been
since you last came home?

00:17:58.610 --> 00:17:59.520
Just to make money,

00:17:59.520 --> 00:18:00.380
was it worth it?

00:18:00.690 --> 00:18:02.690
I've been working hard
to earn money to support you,

00:18:02.690 --> 00:18:04.290
and you're feeling wronged?

00:18:06.450 --> 00:18:08.170
Do you look down on your old man?

00:18:08.170 --> 00:18:08.800
Yes!

00:18:09.520 --> 00:18:10.690
I do look down on you!

00:18:33.800 --> 00:18:35.330
I want to go out for some air.

00:18:47.100 --> 00:18:47.930
What's wrong?

00:18:48.210 --> 00:18:49.280
How did you fall?

00:18:49.450 --> 00:18:50.210
What happened?

00:18:50.210 --> 00:18:50.690
Come, come.

00:18:50.690 --> 00:18:51.240
Be careful.

00:18:51.240 --> 00:18:52.450
It hurts so much!

00:18:52.890 --> 00:18:54.080
Let me help you up first.

00:18:54.080 --> 00:18:55.540
Did you sprain your ankle?

00:18:55.970 --> 00:18:57.130
Yes!

00:18:57.320 --> 00:18:58.210
Don't move!

00:18:58.520 --> 00:18:59.240
It hurts so much.

00:18:59.240 --> 00:19:00.280
How did you fall?

00:19:00.280 --> 00:19:01.030
Come, come.

00:19:01.320 --> 00:19:02.180
Stand up first.

00:19:03.760 --> 00:19:04.770
Are you okay?

00:19:05.080 --> 00:19:06.370
What... What could be wrong with me?

00:19:06.370 --> 00:19:07.800
Don't be too upset.

00:19:08.000 --> 00:19:08.760
No matter what happens,

00:19:08.760 --> 00:19:10.090
I'll stand by your side.

00:19:11.350 --> 00:19:12.040
You're already like this,

00:19:12.040 --> 00:19:13.240
and you still want to stand by my side?

00:19:13.240 --> 00:19:15.040
I should be the one standing by your side.

00:19:15.040 --> 00:19:15.410
Come.

00:19:16.130 --> 00:19:17.450
Let me help you up first.

00:19:17.450 --> 00:19:18.580
Sit down over there.

00:19:20.130 --> 00:19:20.450
Come.

00:19:20.450 --> 00:19:21.110
Be careful.

00:19:23.040 --> 00:19:23.890
Be careful.

00:19:28.450 --> 00:19:29.000
Xiaole,

00:19:29.240 --> 00:19:31.000
I saw Mr. Tong scolding you.

00:19:31.210 --> 00:19:32.000
It's okay.

00:19:32.080 --> 00:19:33.290
Cry if you want to.

00:19:34.800 --> 00:19:36.410
Who is the one crying now?

00:19:37.850 --> 00:19:38.210
Come.

00:19:38.320 --> 00:19:39.320
Let me take a look.

00:19:40.080 --> 00:19:42.080
Let me take a look. Let me take a look.

00:19:43.760 --> 00:19:45.490
I can't move it. I can't move it.

00:19:46.280 --> 00:19:47.610
This hurts way too much.

00:19:50.610 --> 00:19:51.540
Wait for me here.

00:19:51.610 --> 00:19:54.010
I'll go over there
to buy you some medicine!

00:19:54.800 --> 00:19:55.460
Wait for me!

00:20:06.800 --> 00:20:08.930
Why does it hurt and feel cold?

00:20:33.480 --> 00:20:34.370
Little troublemaker,

00:20:34.370 --> 00:20:35.890
stop messing with my cello.

00:20:35.890 --> 00:20:37.280
I need to put it away.

00:20:37.610 --> 00:20:38.240
Sister,

00:20:38.240 --> 00:20:39.280
you promised

00:20:39.280 --> 00:20:41.040
you'd let me play if you got good grades!

00:20:41.040 --> 00:20:42.760
Why are you going back on your word?

00:20:42.760 --> 00:20:43.970
That was Dad who promised!

00:20:43.970 --> 00:20:44.610
I didn't promise anything!

00:20:44.610 --> 00:20:45.280
Give it to me now!

00:20:45.280 --> 00:20:46.810
I just want to play for a bit!

00:20:46.930 --> 00:20:48.040
Sister, you're a liar!

00:20:48.040 --> 00:20:49.520
You don't keep your word!

00:20:49.760 --> 00:20:50.320
Since the exam is over,

00:20:50.320 --> 00:20:51.780
just let him play for a bit.

00:20:54.850 --> 00:20:55.980
Aunt, why are you...

00:20:56.240 --> 00:20:57.800
why are you so partial?

00:20:58.370 --> 00:20:59.040
Dad!

00:20:59.040 --> 00:21:00.610
I just want to play for a bit!

00:21:00.970 --> 00:21:01.560
Give it to me!

00:21:01.560 --> 00:21:02.210
Get lost!

00:21:02.450 --> 00:21:03.040
Dad!

00:21:03.210 --> 00:21:03.690
Dad!

00:21:03.760 --> 00:21:04.320
Dad!

00:21:04.320 --> 00:21:04.800
Dad!

00:21:04.930 --> 00:21:05.450
Dad!

00:21:05.450 --> 00:21:05.970
Dad!

00:21:06.130 --> 00:21:06.690
Dad!

00:21:06.690 --> 00:21:07.210
Dad!

00:21:08.320 --> 00:21:10.120
What are you arguing about here?

00:21:18.690 --> 00:21:19.890
You've gone too far.

00:21:22.000 --> 00:21:22.610
Xuan!

00:21:23.040 --> 00:21:23.760
Xuan!

00:21:24.240 --> 00:21:25.840
Go apologize to your sister!

00:21:27.850 --> 00:21:28.690
Lan.

00:21:32.850 --> 00:21:33.410
Yi Lan!

00:21:36.450 --> 00:21:37.700
Where did you get the coat?

00:21:37.700 --> 00:21:38.930
I went to get it.

00:21:39.240 --> 00:21:39.970
Here. Here. Here.

00:21:39.970 --> 00:21:41.800
Let me apply the medicine for you first.

00:21:41.800 --> 00:21:42.530
Bear with it.

00:21:46.130 --> 00:21:46.970
Bear with it.

00:21:47.480 --> 00:21:49.140
Does it really hurt this much?

00:21:50.410 --> 00:21:52.900
My brother broke my cello!

00:21:54.170 --> 00:21:55.560
The cello is broken?

00:21:56.240 --> 00:21:57.240
Can it be fixed?

00:21:57.240 --> 00:21:58.090
I don't know.

00:21:58.480 --> 00:21:59.810
It's all my dad's fault.

00:22:00.370 --> 00:22:02.370
He got drunk and didn't control him.

00:22:05.690 --> 00:22:06.130
Here.

00:22:08.930 --> 00:22:10.390
You're already like this,

00:22:10.480 --> 00:22:11.800
and you still brought plum syrup?

00:22:11.800 --> 00:22:13.760
You drink it every year
and you never get tired of it.

00:22:13.760 --> 00:22:15.210
There are steamed buns too.

00:22:15.210 --> 00:22:16.610
I specially brought them for you.

00:22:16.610 --> 00:22:18.010
I know you haven't eaten.

00:22:18.650 --> 00:22:19.170
Eat.

00:22:21.800 --> 00:22:22.860
They're still hot.

00:22:23.080 --> 00:22:25.040
These are
my brother's favorite steamed buns.

00:22:25.040 --> 00:22:26.040
I packed them all.

00:22:26.040 --> 00:22:27.300
I won't let him eat any.

00:22:29.240 --> 00:22:29.970
Yi Lan.

00:22:31.370 --> 00:22:33.200
Don't be too good to me.

00:22:33.480 --> 00:22:34.940
Is being good to you wrong?

00:22:35.930 --> 00:22:36.990
What are you doing?

00:22:37.320 --> 00:22:38.800
Shutting you up.

00:22:44.890 --> 00:22:46.970
Sister, I'm sorry.

00:22:47.450 --> 00:22:50.280
I'll never touch your cello again.

00:22:51.520 --> 00:22:52.560
Brother.

00:22:53.480 --> 00:22:54.480
It's okay.

00:22:55.410 --> 00:22:56.010
Let's hug.

00:23:00.850 --> 00:23:02.080
Brother.

00:23:02.610 --> 00:23:04.450
Let's never argue again, okay?

00:23:04.450 --> 00:23:05.170
Okay!

00:23:05.320 --> 00:23:06.470
Okay?

00:23:06.500 --> 00:23:07.300
Okay!

00:23:07.800 --> 00:23:09.800
Is it okay if I eat your steamed buns?

00:23:10.480 --> 00:23:12.410
It's good that you're okay with it.

00:23:14.520 --> 00:23:17.080
You're the best brother in the world.

00:23:32.170 --> 00:23:33.320
Are you okay?

00:23:48.210 --> 00:23:49.410
Let me tell you.

00:23:49.520 --> 00:23:51.080
This is nothing.

00:23:51.450 --> 00:23:52.710
Is this even a problem?

00:23:52.760 --> 00:23:53.740
Let's go again.

00:23:54.210 --> 00:23:55.320
Take it easy.

00:23:55.480 --> 00:23:56.650
Still half a glass, okay?

00:23:56.650 --> 00:23:56.970
Okay.

00:23:56.970 --> 00:23:57.970
I won't bully you.

00:23:58.040 --> 00:23:58.410
No problem.

00:23:58.410 --> 00:24:00.000
We're good.

00:24:13.280 --> 00:24:14.760
Are you okay, Tong?

00:24:14.760 --> 00:24:15.800
I'm fine.

00:24:29.450 --> 00:24:30.040
Xiaole.

00:24:30.850 --> 00:24:32.170
You haven't eaten, have you?

00:24:32.170 --> 00:24:33.520
I made dumplings for you.

00:24:33.520 --> 00:24:34.000
Mom,

00:24:34.210 --> 00:24:35.450
I just ate outside.

00:24:36.410 --> 00:24:37.040
Xiaole.

00:24:39.560 --> 00:24:40.720
I shouldn't have...

00:24:41.760 --> 00:24:42.960
slapped you just now.

00:24:47.520 --> 00:24:49.040
Mr. Bu told me everything

00:24:49.610 --> 00:24:50.760
about you at school.

00:24:51.880 --> 00:24:53.040
You like photography.

00:24:53.040 --> 00:24:54.840
You could have told me directly.

00:24:55.000 --> 00:24:56.930
I didn't insist you study Finance.

00:24:57.080 --> 00:24:58.210
I just wanted you...

00:24:58.240 --> 00:24:59.280
to have a goal,

00:24:59.280 --> 00:25:00.680
something to strive for.

00:25:04.130 --> 00:25:04.970
Look, Xiaole.

00:25:07.210 --> 00:25:08.480
This is a camera your dad asked someone

00:25:08.480 --> 00:25:10.080
to bring from abroad for you.

00:25:10.080 --> 00:25:11.950
We wanted to surprise you.

00:25:16.580 --> 00:25:18.840
Tong, do you have something to say to him?

00:25:19.370 --> 00:25:19.800
Right?

00:25:25.720 --> 00:25:26.180
It's...

00:25:27.140 --> 00:25:28.870
not that I don't care about you.

00:25:29.040 --> 00:25:31.300
Every time I asked if you needed company,

00:25:32.320 --> 00:25:32.980
you said...

00:25:33.800 --> 00:25:34.280
no.

00:25:35.320 --> 00:25:36.130
And...

00:25:36.210 --> 00:25:38.040
we argued whenever we met.

00:25:39.480 --> 00:25:40.280
I always felt

00:25:40.280 --> 00:25:41.480
you found me annoying

00:25:41.760 --> 00:25:43.220
and you liked being alone.

00:25:46.520 --> 00:25:47.210
Look at our son.

00:25:47.210 --> 00:25:48.280
We don't usually supervise him,

00:25:48.280 --> 00:25:49.520
but his grades are good.

00:25:49.520 --> 00:25:49.970
Right?

00:25:50.280 --> 00:25:52.210
Your dad was worried
you found him annoying.

00:25:52.210 --> 00:25:53.560
You always ignored him at home.

00:25:53.560 --> 00:25:53.930
Right?

00:25:53.930 --> 00:25:54.990
He overthought it.

00:25:55.130 --> 00:25:55.850
Don't be angry.

00:25:55.850 --> 00:25:56.480
Xiaole.

00:25:57.320 --> 00:25:58.580
You like photography.

00:25:59.370 --> 00:26:00.500
After you graduate,

00:26:00.720 --> 00:26:02.580
we'll open a photography studio.

00:26:03.450 --> 00:26:04.760
With the money your mom and I earn,

00:26:04.760 --> 00:26:06.040
we can open a big one for you.

00:26:06.040 --> 00:26:07.240
Hurry and make him write it down,

00:26:07.240 --> 00:26:08.900
so he won't go back on his word.

00:26:10.040 --> 00:26:10.610
Mom.

00:26:11.080 --> 00:26:12.010
Hold this for me.

00:26:15.240 --> 00:26:15.850
Dad.

00:26:17.560 --> 00:26:18.690
Drink this.

00:26:19.000 --> 00:26:20.590
Drink less alcohol in the future.

00:26:20.590 --> 00:26:22.050
It's bad for your stomach.

00:26:22.720 --> 00:26:23.780
Thank you, Xiaole.

00:26:25.610 --> 00:26:27.800
From now on,
I'll take good care of the family

00:26:27.800 --> 00:26:29.200
and take good care of you.

00:26:32.320 --> 00:26:33.280
Give me a hug.

00:26:33.720 --> 00:26:34.940
Come. Let me lift you up.

00:26:34.940 --> 00:26:35.760
Dad! Dad!

00:26:35.760 --> 00:26:36.240
Come on.

00:26:36.240 --> 00:26:37.370
I'm... I'm too old for this!

00:26:37.370 --> 00:26:38.370
Put me down!

00:26:38.370 --> 00:26:39.240
Put me down!

00:26:40.320 --> 00:26:41.870
Mom, look at him!

00:26:42.040 --> 00:26:43.650
Put me down!

00:26:43.680 --> 00:26:44.710
No.

00:26:45.040 --> 00:26:46.080
Come on.

00:27:47.080 --> 00:27:48.240
Who has a lighter?

00:27:50.760 --> 00:27:52.020
Where did you get that?

00:27:58.650 --> 00:27:59.480
Pass it along.

00:28:13.650 --> 00:28:14.480
Ning.

00:28:17.720 --> 00:28:20.450
The school at night
is actually quite beautiful.

00:28:36.040 --> 00:28:37.320
-Chen Fan!
-Chen Fan!

00:28:37.320 --> 00:28:38.850
You really are annoying!

00:28:38.850 --> 00:28:40.380
Who are you trying to scare?

00:28:40.520 --> 00:28:42.080
You're going to attract Director Hu here.

00:28:42.080 --> 00:28:43.320
Ning,

00:28:43.690 --> 00:28:46.150
I've never seen you
smile so happily before.

00:28:48.800 --> 00:28:50.040
Because being with you guys

00:28:50.040 --> 00:28:51.300
makes me really happy.

00:28:51.560 --> 00:28:53.350
If you're happy,
you should laugh out loud.

00:28:53.350 --> 00:28:55.480
You look really pretty when you smile.

00:29:01.690 --> 00:29:02.520
At this hour,

00:29:02.520 --> 00:29:04.250
Director Hu is still on patrol?

00:29:05.850 --> 00:29:06.690
Hello!

00:29:08.480 --> 00:29:11.140
-Zhao Zhenghao?
-Why are you guys here so early?

00:29:12.760 --> 00:29:13.850
Qiao Mengmeng.

00:29:14.370 --> 00:29:15.320
It wasn't me.

00:29:16.320 --> 00:29:17.440
I invited him.

00:29:17.720 --> 00:29:18.940
Isn't Zhenghao

00:29:18.960 --> 00:29:20.150
part of our group?

00:29:20.240 --> 00:29:21.240
Of course.

00:29:23.760 --> 00:29:25.170
Look! Fireworks!

00:29:27.130 --> 00:29:28.190
Quick, make a wish!

00:29:34.760 --> 00:29:36.850
I hope I can
successfully pass the art exam

00:29:36.850 --> 00:29:38.290
and get admitted to Hailan University.

00:29:38.290 --> 00:29:40.040
♪ Dusk gently fell on the coastline ♪

00:29:40.040 --> 00:29:41.080
Why did you eavesdrop?

00:29:41.080 --> 00:29:41.930
It won't come true if you eavesdrop!

00:29:41.930 --> 00:29:43.000
♪ The quietly passing breeze
gave the clouds a kiss ♪

00:29:43.000 --> 00:29:44.480
You are so annoying!

